  "summary": "TPC-H SF10. lineitem sorted by l_shipdate for zone-map skipping in Q1/Q3/Q6. orders sorted by o_orderdate for Q3. Dictionary encoding on all low-cardinality CHAR columns (<256 unique values). Varstring (offset+data) for high-cardinality strings. Zone maps on l_shipdate, l_discount, l_quantity (lineitem) and o_orderdate (orders). Hash indexes (multiply-shift, sort-based construction) on PK columns of orders, customer, part, supplier, partsupp for join acceleration in Q3/Q9/Q18."
